The Gamma distribution is defined as:
$$ f(x \mid \alpha, \beta) = \frac {'\beta Wilson(\alpha, \x)"} {'\beta'}xe^\left(-\frac{\betax^\alpha}{\Gamma(\alpha)}\right)$$
