If you want to support default values, you should overload the constructor, e.g.
public record MyRecord(Set&lt;String&gt; strings, boolean required) {
    public MyRecord {
        strings = Set.copyOf(strings); // enforce non-null immutable set
    }
    public MyRecord() {
        this(Set.of(), true);
    }
}

